      "content": "i mean i know you're an ai but i'm trying to save money and avoid a clinic visit if i can. it doesn't feel like an emergency or anything, just annoying. if i just use the lubricating drops for a few days, is there any reason that would be bad? i feel like it's mostly just irritation from the screen.",
