      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay that makes sense. so if i just stick to one brand of the standard lubricating drops for like 3 or 4 days, it should be fine to just manage it at home? if it's just dry eyes it shouldn't get worse by waiting a few days, right? i'd rather just try the drops first before making a whole thing out of it.",
